gr.ntua.vision.monitoring.model
Interface Location

All Superinterfaces:
JSONExchanged
All Known Implementing Classes:
LocationImpl
public interface Location
extends JSONExchanged

The location of an event generation or target. Note that depending on the event type and actual location, some of the information contained here is meaningless. Therefore there are cases in which the methods will return nulls to indicate that no relevant data are associated.
